RCS & RDS Borrows 101 Million Euros From Banca Comerciala Romana

-- B y   I r i n a   S a v u
-- 
2011-12-05T07:15:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-05/rcs-rds-borrows-101-million-euros-from-banca-comerciala-romana.html
RCS & RDS SA , a Romanian
telecommunications company, borrowed 101 million euros ($135
million) from Banca Comerciala Romana SA to refinance debt, the
Bucharest-based bank said yesterday in an e-mail.  The loan is the first installment of a five-year, 300
million-euro syndicated credit from BCR,  Credit Suisse Group AG (CSGN) 
and CEC Bank SA, according to the statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Irina Savu in Bucharest at 
 isavu@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James M. Gomez at 
 jagomez@bloomberg.net  